Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Applied AI Engineer position with SOCOTEC. I bring over three years of professional experience in AI-driven systems, machine learning pipelines, and conversational AI, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

Through my experience across multiple engineering roles, I have built and delivered production-grade AI systems that directly reflect the technical depth this position demands. As a Software Engineer at Sperse, I designed and deployed an AI-driven conversational system that translates natural-language intents into validated tool calls across 1,000+ endpoints — requiring rigorous data preprocessing, model evaluation, and production deployment workflows. I built machine learning pipelines using LangChain and LangGraph to orchestrate multi-agent workflows, enabling scalable AI model integration with reliable coordination across complex customer interactions. To ensure production readiness, I implemented comprehensive model monitoring and observability using Langfuse and LangSmith, covering tracing, structured logs, and evaluation hooks, while optimizing model performance through hyperparameter tuning and prompt routing to reduce latency by 60% and LLM API costs by 50%. Prior to Sperse, as a Software Engineer at Qualitest, I built an internal support chatbot using LangChain and RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) with PostgreSQL vector store, implementing NLP and conversational AI workflows that reduced ticket resolution time by 20%. I also designed a cloud-agnostic Storage Service using Python, PostgreSQL, and Redis handling file operations across Google Cloud Storage, AWS S3, and MinIO, and contributed to an Identity & Access Management platform built with React, Spring Boot, and AWS, following agile development methodologies and supporting thousands of users across 30+ applications. Together, these roles have prepared me to design, develop, and deploy AI models that enhance SOCOTEC's chatbot program and other AI-driven solutions while collaborating effectively with cross-functional teams.

